Package io.craigmiller160.stockmarket.util

Contains utility classes with constant values and other resources that need to be shared between various packages in this program.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Fonts
    A utility class containing the fonts used in this program.
    Language
    A wrapper class to allow multiple GUI classes to share a ResourceBundle that contains the program's language file.
    LoggerCSVFormat
    A Logger format that formats a log record for output to a CSV file.
    LoggerFormat
    A format designed to display key information for all entries into this program's log.

Package io.craigmiller160.stockmarket.util Description

Contains utility classes with constant values and other resources that need to be shared between various packages in this program. Classes in this package include fonts, locale-based configuration, and formats for the program's logger output.
Since:
Version 2.0
Author:
